    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The exterior displays a healthy shine, though upon close inspection, you will find some minor stone chips on the front bumper and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful ownership. The interior is clean and smoke-free, showing only minimal wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and is ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
