    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a peerless example of automotive excellence. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting a flawless exterior finish and an interior devoid of wear. Meticulously maintained and mechanically beyond reproach, it offers a driving experience indistinguishable from its original delivery. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector to acquire a truly pristine specimen.",
